{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2790,"text":"Hello."},{"time":4000,"text":"I'm a toy developer."},{"time":6845,"text":"With a dream of creating new toys\nthat have never been seen before,"},{"time":10899,"text":"I began working at a toy company\nnine years ago."},{"time":14026,"text":"When I first started working there,"},{"time":16062,"text":"I proposed many new ideas\nto my boss every day."},{"time":20020,"text":"However, my boss always asked"},{"time":22838,"text":"if I had the data to prove it would sell,"},{"time":25442,"text":"and asked me to think of product\ndevelopment after analyzing market data."},{"time":28875,"text":"Data, data, data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30539,"text":"So I analyzed the market data\nbefore thinking of a product."},{"time":34788,"text":"However, I was unable to think\nof anything new at that moment."},{"time":39080,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":40542,"text":"My ideas were unoriginal."},{"time":42591,"text":"I wasn't getting any new ideas\nand I grew tired of thinking."},{"time":46904,"text":"It was so hard that I became this skinny."},{"time":51585,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":53582,"text":"It's true.\n(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56224,"text":"You've all probably had\nsimilar experiences and felt this way too."},{"time":60279,"text":"Your boss was being difficult.\nThe data was difficult."},{"time":62891,"text":"You become sick of thinking."},{"time":64682,"text":"Now, I throw out the data."},{"time":67587,"text":"It's my dream to create new toys."},{"time":70596,"text":"And now, instead of data,"},{"time":72824,"text":"I'm using a game called Shiritori\nto come up with new ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77012,"text":"I would like to introduce\nthis method today."},{"time":80580,"text":"What is Shiritori?"},{"time":82701,"text":"Take apple, elephant \nand trumpet, for example."},{"time":85166,"text":"It's a game where \nyou take turns saying words"},{"time":87400,"text":"that start with the last letter\nof the previous word."},{"time":89962,"text":"It's the same in Japanese and English."},{"time":91864,"text":"You can play Shiritori as you like:"},{"time":94158,"text":"\"neko, kora, raibu, burashi,\" etc, etc.\n[Cat, cola, concert, brush]"},{"time":97396,"text":"Many random words will come out."},{"time":100084,"text":"You force those words to connect to what\nyou want to think of and form ideas."},{"time":105174,"text":"In my case, for example,\nsince I want to think of toys,"},{"time":108777,"text":"what could a toy cat be?"},{"time":111660,"text":"A cat that lands after doing\na somersault from a high place?"},{"time":115227,"text":"How about a toy with cola?"},{"time":117353,"text":"A toy gun where you shoot cola\nand get someone soaking wet?"},{"time":120354,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":121343,"text":"Ridiculous ideas are okay.\nThe key is to keep them flowing."},{"time":124376,"text":"The more ideas you produce, you're sure\nto come up with some good ones, too."},{"time":129732,"text":"A brush, for example.\nCan we make a toothbrush into a toy?"},{"time":134598,"text":"We could combine\na toothbrush with a guitar and --"},{"time":138464,"text":"(Music noises) --"},{"time":140609,"text":"you've got a toy you can play with\nwhile brushing your teeth."},{"time":143765,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":145531,"text":"Kids who don't like to brush\ntheir teeth might begin to like it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149484,"text":"Can we make a hat into a toy?"},{"time":152706,"text":"How about something like a roulette game,\nwhere you try the hat on one by one,"},{"time":156757,"text":"and then, when someone puts it on,\na scary alien breaks through the top"},{"time":161641,"text":"screaming, \"Ahh!\""},{"time":163635,"text":"I wonder if there would be\na demand for this at parties?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166630,"text":"Ideas that didn't come out while you stare\nat the data will start to come out."},{"time":171873,"text":"Actually, this bubble wrap,\nwhich is used to pack fragile objects,"},{"time":177745,"text":"combined with a toy,\nmade Mugen Pop Pop,"},{"time":182551,"text":"a toy where you can pop\nthe bubbles as much as you like."},{"time":185823,"text":"It was a big hit when it reached stores."},{"time":188013,"text":"Data had nothing to do with its success."},{"time":190960,"text":"Although it's only popping bubbles,"},{"time":193662,"text":"it's a great way to kill time,"},{"time":195716,"text":"so please pass this around"},{"time":197770,"text":"amongst yourselves today and play with it."},{"time":200325,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204856,"text":"Anyway, you continue to come up with\nuseless ideas."},{"time":207544,"text":"Think up many trivial ideas, everyone."},{"time":209894,"text":"If you base your ideas on data analysis\nand know what you're aiming for,"},{"time":213591,"text":"you'll end up trying too hard,"},{"time":216060,"text":"and you can't produce new ideas."},{"time":218002,"text":"Even if you know what your aim is,"},{"time":220235,"text":"think of ideas as freely as if you were\nthrowing darts with your eyes closed."},{"time":224121,"text":"If you do this, you surely will hit\nsomewhere near the center."},{"time":227272,"text":"At least one will."},{"time":228860,"text":"That's the one you should choose."},{"time":230907,"text":"If you do so, that idea will be in demand"},{"time":233541,"text":"and, moreover, it will be brand new."},{"time":236325,"text":"That is how I think of new ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238441,"text":"It doesn't have to be Shiritori;\nthere are many different methods."},{"time":241633,"text":"You just have to choose words at random."},{"time":243543,"text":"You can flip through a dictionary\nand choose words at random."},{"time":246490,"text":"For example, you could look up two\nrandom letters and gather the results"},{"time":250904,"text":"or go to the store\nand connect product names"},{"time":254552,"text":"with what you want to think of."},{"time":257992,"text":"The point is to gather random words,"},{"time":261142,"text":"not information from the category\nyou're thinking for."},{"time":264487,"text":"If you do this, the ingredients for\nthe association of ideas are collected"},{"time":270467,"text":"and form connections\nthat will produce many ideas."},{"time":273356,"text":"The greatest advantage to this method\nis the continuous flow of images."},{"time":277245,"text":"Because you're thinking\nof one word after another,"},{"time":280218,"text":"the image of the previous word\nis still with you."},{"time":282884,"text":"That image will automatically\nbe related with future words."},{"time":285649,"text":"Unconsciously, a concert will\nbe connected to a brush"},{"time":288171,"text":"and a roulette game\nwill be connected to a hat."},{"time":290360,"text":"You wouldn't even realize it."},{"time":291740,"text":"You can come up with ideas that\nyou wouldn't have thought of otherwise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295081,"text":"This method is, of course,\nnot just for toys."},{"time":297181,"text":"You can collect ideas for books, apps,\nevents, and many other projects."},{"time":301892,"text":"I hope you all try this method."},{"time":306170,"text":"There are futures that are born from data."},{"time":309089,"text":"However, using this silly game\ncalled Shiritori,"},{"time":313859,"text":"I look forward to\nthe exciting future you will create,"},{"time":316959,"text":"a future you couldn't even imagine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320490,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322891,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}